lead_paragraph: England striker Harry Kane will return to Tottenham Hotspur's squad for Sunday's North London derby at Arsenal, manager Mauricio Pochettino said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Kane Back in Tottenham Squad for Arsenal Game
